ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of LUCIO RAGAGNIN of Vaughan, Ontario, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective June 22, 2019, in the place of Aditya Jha, whose term has expired.
